# Technical Stack
Referenced in: [001-project-overview.mdc](001-project-overview.mdc)

## Core Runtime
- **Language**: Java 21 (LTS)
- **Framework**: Spring Boot 3.x
- **Build Tool**: Gradle (Groovy DSL)

## Persistence
- **Database**: MySQL 8.0 or PostgreSQL 15 (Targeting relational DB)
- **ORM**: Spring Data JPA (Hibernate)
- **Dynamic Query**: QueryDSL 5.x
- **Migrations**: Flyway or Liquibase (Recommended for schema management)

## Caching & Messaging
- **Caching**: Redis (Spring Data Redis)
- **Message Queue**: Apache Kafka (Spring Kafka) for event-driven architecture and Saga pattern

## Security
- **Authentication**: Spring Security 6.x
- **Token**: JWT (JSON Web Token) for stateless authentication
- **Encryption**: BCrypt for password hashing

## Documentation
- **API Docs**: SpringDoc OpenAPI (Swagger UI)

## Testing
- **Unit**: JUnit 5, Mockito
- **Integration**: Spring Boot Test, Testcontainers (for DB/Redis/Kafka)

## External Services
- **AI/ML Integration**: OpenAI API / Hugging Face API (via RestClient/WebClient)
